{"root":{"data":{"id":"dh0oixst3t40","created":1773306034199,"text":"测试数据的几大原因"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oncjdnq80","created":1773306379737,"text":"研究生阶段的能力铺垫","layout_mind_offset":{"x":19.166664299037876,"y":78.49999927481011},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0p1qo7wps0","created":1773307507603,"text":"mems的使用练习，后续实验使用mems能够迅速上手","layout_right_offset":{"x":68.50000155965483,"y":-26.083334048174947}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0tr7sycbc0","created":1773320788439,"text":"分支主题","layout_right_offset":{"x":91.00000180800782,"y":0}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dh0onejsx5k0","created":1773306384116,"text":"加强毕设本身的理解","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-48.00000095367437,"y":93.00000184774422}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0ongf51wo0","created":1773306388188,"text":"实际技术需求","layout_mind_offset":{"x":874.0000139276212,"y":-164.75000299389205},"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ozlkz49k0","created":1773307339794,"text":"多轴运动\n楼梯+斜坡实验\n上下楼梯（3-5层）和上下斜坡（坡度5°-15°）\n高度误差、水平投影误差、垂直方向零速检测率","layout_right_offset":{"x":520.4166577859902,"y":152.9166645908527}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0oznr9vp40","created":1773307344529,"text":"变速折返跑（考虑到变速情况对零速检测\n的影响，同时折返时刻急停可能会误差）","layout_right_offset":{"x":84.58333323606223,"y":126.66666495717286}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0uf60heq80","created":1773322665280,"text":"圆形轨迹多圈验证，","layout_right_offset":{"x":94.99999811251996,"y":128.33333078357953}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vg6pebs00","created":1773325566260,"text":"航向误差\n长距离/多转弯实验\n设计包含多个直角弯的闭合路径（如矩形走5圈），观察每圈结束时的航向偏差累积\n每圈航向角误差、终点闭合误差","layout_right_offset":{"x":109.9999978144968,"y":-206.6666625605697}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0up10yezc0","created":1773323438066,"text":"增加不同状态下的对比实验：我和上一个同学的步长\n不同，验证不同步长下的零速检测结果以及轨迹解算（检验算法对不同步长的适应能力，h）","layout_right_offset":{"x":15.833333018753422,"y":14.166666385200358}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0veukyr740","created":1773325461507,"text":"多步速对比实验","layout_right_offset":{"x":87.49999826153152,"y":-497.66662816869024}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dh0vf76wwrk0","created":1773325488955,"text":"复杂步态实验\n包含正常走、倒走、侧身走、爬行（如可行）、跳跃等多种步态模式的复合路径","layout_right_offset":{"x":88.33333157830802,"y":-503.16665953066746}},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}